WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.000
I'm just a girl that loves fashion.

00:02.001 --> 00:05.761
So when we got invited to the CFDA Awards by Ralph Lauren,

00:05.762 --> 00:09.141
I obviously said yes and got on the next flight out.

00:09.160 --> 00:10.840
Tonight we're getting ready for it.

00:10.841 --> 00:12.161
My nails were embarrassing,

00:12.162 --> 00:13.761
so I had to get my nails done.

00:13.762 --> 00:17.321
Hair and makeup, I'm very selective with who I let touch my face,

00:17.322 --> 00:18.881
but Yasmin, my makeup artist,

00:18.882 --> 00:21.481
just got back from tour, so I was so happy.

00:21.482 --> 00:24.041
Made it out to New York to glam me for tonight.

00:24.042 --> 00:26.361
Little whimsy Lou came with us to New York.

00:26.362 --> 00:29.201
Obviously had to hang out while we were doing glam.

00:29.202 --> 00:30.921
Got the dress tailored the night before,

00:30.922 --> 00:33.441
so we were trying it on to see whether it fit.

00:33.442 --> 00:36.241
So glad it fits so well. Right before leaving,

00:36.242 --> 00:37.841
lucky got whimsy to sleep,

00:37.842 --> 00:39.081
did the finishing touches,

00:39.082 --> 00:40.561
and then we were out the door.

00:40.562 --> 00:42.601
I always get a little bit of social anxiety

00:42.602 --> 00:44.041
when it comes to events like these,

00:44.042 --> 00:47.001
so I'm so glad that lucky and I can do them together.

00:47.002 --> 00:51.281
We got there. I was so in awe of this museum and the Dinosaur skeletons,

00:51.282 --> 00:53.121
and little me was geeking out,

00:53.122 --> 00:55.241
and just a little science girl at heart.

00:55.242 --> 00:57.201
We walked the carpet, got the pictures,

00:57.202 --> 01:00.601
and then it was time to sit down and have my first chicken pot pie

01:00.602 --> 01:01.767
and enjoy the rest of the night.
